targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  occurred_at AS "time",
  detail+0.0 as "v4rtt_srv_max"
FROM diagnosis_logs
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(occurred_at) and
  log_type = "v4rtt_srv_max" and
  target = "$target_v4rtt_srv" and
  log_campaign_uuid in (
    select
      log_campaign_uuid
    from log_campaigns
    where mac_addr = "$sindanClientID" )
ORDER BY occurred_at

panels.description: SNR should be 20 or more for a data network.

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  occurred_at AS "time",
  detail+0.0 as "rssi"
FROM diagnosis_logs
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(occurred_at) and
  log_type = "rssi" and
  log_campaign_uuid in (
    select
      log_campaign_uuid
    from log_campaigns
    where mac_addr = "$sindanClientID" )
ORDER BY occurred_at

SELECT
  occurred_at AS "time",
  detail+0.0 as "noise"
FROM diagnosis_logs
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(occurred_at) and
  log_type = "noise" and
  log_campaign_uuid in (
    select
      log_campaign_uuid
    from log_campaigns
    where mac_addr = "$sindanClientID" )
ORDER BY occurred_at

SELECT
  a.occurred_at AS "time",
  (a.detail+0.0) - (b.detail+0.0) AS "SNR"
FROM
  (
  SELECT log_campaign_uuid, occurred_at, detail
  FROM diagnosis_logs
  WHERE
    $__timeFilter(occurred_at) AND
    log_type = "RSSI" AND
    log_campaign_uuid in (
      SELECT log_campaign_uuid
      FROM log_campaigns
      WHERE mac_addr = "$sindanClientID"
    )
  ) AS a
LEFT JOIN
  (
  SELECT log_campaign_uuid, occurred_at, detail
  FROM diagnosis_logs
  WHERE
    $__timeFilter(occurred_at) AND
    log_type = "noise" AND
    log_campaign_uuid in (
      SELECT log_campaign_uuid
      FROM log_campaigns
      WHERE mac_addr = "$sindanClientID"
    )
  ) As b
ON a.log_campaign_uuid = b.log_campaign_uuid
